OL,4,CTravel firms warned over summer holiday
OL,5,Crefunds
OL,6, Travel companies have been warned they
OL,7, must be ready to refund consumers if
OL,8, foreign holidays are cancelled by the
OL,9, coronavirus pandemic this summer.
OL,11,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,12,Fsaid it had reminded package holiday
OL,13,Ffirms of their legal obligations.
OL,15,FIn 2020, cancelled trips resulted in
OL,16,F23,000 complaints to the competition
OL,17,Fwatchdog.
OL,19,FThe CMA said it had taken action
OL,20,Fagainst five big firms, which had now
OL,21,Frefunded a total of #200m.
